od po must read"},{"pid":"06238aba365946b05b90ea369f988c5c52043565","tid":1821750,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343e99893246fbf94ab6780d53708a2fd06ec486","tid":1821750,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d1832ae14eb5eaacd5551d7255170f8496f1f50","tid":1821750,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另一種是誘使民主擁護者行反民主之實，使他們自行破壞民主。</blockquote><br />\n擊倒魔王<br />\n但係自己都變成魔王"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"從來要撃敗魔王都只有成為另一個魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進撃的巨人教識你架啦，要報仇，就要變成比巨人更勁既巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.history.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cg_faces:center%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_768/MTU3ODc5MDgyNjc0ODkwNDYz/by-john-trumbull-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2F.image%2Far_16%3A9%252Cc_fill%252Ccs_srgb%252Cfl_progressive%252Cg_faces%3Acenter%252Cq_auto%3Agood%252Cw_768%2FMTU3ODc5MDgyNjc0ODkwNDYz%2Fby-john-trumbull-3.jpg&h=a44d8145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用契約黎限制自己同往後繼任者既權力<br />\n美國開國先賢的確係歷史既偶然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae087ffdc347311557012a7a1389a8b604cdcf5","tid":1821750,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06238aba365946b05b90ea369f988c5c52043565","tid":1821750,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343e99893246fbf94ab6780d53708a2fd06ec486","tid":1821750,"uid":88134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d1832ae14eb5eaacd5551d7255170f8496f1f50","tid":1821750,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另一種是誘使民主擁護者行反民主之實，使他們自行破壞民主。</blockquote><br />\n擊倒魔王<br />\n但係自己都變成魔王"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:30:33.000Z","msg":"從來要撃敗魔王都只有成為另一個魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進撃的巨人教識你架啦，要報仇，就要變成比巨人更勁既巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.history.com/.image/ar_16:9%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cg_faces:center%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_768/MTU3ODc5MDgyNjc0ODkwNDYz/by-john-trumbull-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2F.image%2Far_16%3A9%252Cc_fill%252Ccs_srgb%252Cfl_progressive%252Cg_faces%3Acenter%252Cq_auto%3Agood%252Cw_768%2FMTU3ODc5MDgyNjc0ODkwNDYz%2Fby-john-trumbull-3.jpg&h=a44d8145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用契約黎限制自己同往後繼任者既權力<br />\n美國開國先賢的確係歷史既偶然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"可唔可解釋多小小？<br />\n無讀歷史不過都知美國開國元勳好勁"},{"pid":"1c0fb092127679c795849004c48d0444227e2116","tid":1821750,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"睇唔明呢篇文有咩地方好。換個場景換個數字人物呢篇文可以套入大部份國家選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n邊個輸左唔係返回潛伏狀態，伺候下一個證明自己才是正確的時機，邊個黨係輸一次選舉就氣數已盡。<br />\n<br />\n每次戰勝完都叫人唔好打飛機，其實未嬴，之後講句唯有失敗可推動改革，又話下一次的失敗就是徹底的潰敗。總之嬴就話唔好打飛機，輸就話一早話左叫你咪撚打飛機。<br />\n<br />\n你覺得好中係因為呢堆說話空泛到同星座運程同level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}